    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/krabi-seabass-hotel/hotel/krabi-th.html",
    "name": "Krabi SeaBass Hotel",
    "detail": "We stayed here 2 nights in Krabi at the Seabass and compared to most of the hotels i've stayed in Thailand (so far its been 12) This has been one of the best. Close to the night market. Very clean. Friendly staff. Very comfortable bed. a REAL shower. Let us check in early. The daily housekeeping was one of the best i've seen. Hotel looked brand new. The only bad thing I have to say about the hotel was they charge 500 Bhat for a taxi to the airport. I walked 5 minutes down the street and found one for 300. I really recommend this to anyone doing a short layover in Krabi town. ",
